{"id": "1229475816258142220", "channel_id": "1229473538474512466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168245675419508766", "author_name": "arielsred", "author_bot": false, "content": "【4-12  她】孩子向母親伸出雙手，祈求一個充滿疼痛的擁抱。即使注射針刺破纖嫩表皮，手術刀劃開潔白肌膚，束縛帶捆紮柔弱關節。蔓延的無邊疼痛依然無法阻止她們相擁。因為，這是最溫暖的擁抱。自胚胎脫出母體，生出嫌隙，磨出鋒銳，互相傷害，最終回歸輕密，融為一體。", "timestamp": "2024-04-15T16:57:57.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1229475815738052618", "filename": "4-12.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1197242, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1229473538474512466/1229475815738052618/4-12.jpg?ex=69cca5d5&is=69cb5455&hm=673661e09b2a85365c1f8eebd5a9d72feb2e74834122c4f918fe5eebcfe964df&"}, {"id": "1229475816359071835", "filename": "4-12.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1312256, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1229473538474512466/1229475816359071835/4-12.jpg?ex=69cca5d5&is=69cb5455&hm=b3a872c76ccba780d6d2ed4ca1b54143d88b4d5ba6d9a5ddad2ec6f217a4cdfe&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1229473538474512466", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "§【主線劇情】《第四章 於無聲處》§", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
